<plot>Stripping war to its barest representation, "The Last Drop" chronicles the journey of a man dying of thirst in the scorching desert. As Wandering Man's body and mind breakdown from the unrelenting heat, he stumbles across his salvation: a bucket of water. But that water belongs to another man. Will the men share this treasure - or will it tear them apart?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?569369</url></doc>
